creator: Puget Sound Energy
descriptionHtml:
The new Puget Sound Energy mobile app makes accessing your account information on the go easier than ever. The new mobile app offers increased self-service capabilities, allowing you to: manage your account, review your account summary and make payment with just one click. Also, you can track and report power outages in your neighborhood and check status and estimated restoration times, all in the palm of your hand.

Manage your account:
• Review your account balance and pay your bills
• View payment and billing history
• Change or update your password or contact information

Stay informed about outages:
• Easily report outages
• View outage status on the map, searching by address, city or ZIP code
• Receive in-app outage status updates
descriptionShort: Pay your bill or report an outage

title: myPSE from Puget Sound Energy

creator: Puget Sound Energy
descriptionHtml:
The myPSE app provides easy access to your account when you're on the go. Check your balance and make a payment with just one click. Track & report power outages in your neighborhood and check on restoration times, all in the palm of your hand.

Manage your account:
• Review your account balance, prior month’s charges and pay your bill
• Use and securely save your preferred payment method – eCheck, debit, credit, PayPal or Venmo
• Manage personal preferences - select your desired bill due date or enroll in paperless billing
• Change or update your account security, including password and security questions
• Start, stop or move your residential service

Stay informed about outages:
• View outage status on the map, searching by address, city or ZIP code
• Easily report an outage
• Set your preferences to receive outage notifications by email, text or phone
descriptionShort: Pay your bill or report an outage

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• Updated Payment Experience
• Expanded Auto Pay options
• Additional payment choices, including PayPal and Venmo
